        "Description": "Hello, 47,\rWelcome to Isle of Sgàil. Your target is Mr. Winter.\r\rOur client, Mr. Summer is concerned about Mr. Winter&apos;s interest in his son.\rAs the data suggests, an accident met at least three of Mr. Winter&apos;s previous boyfriends, during a time in which they wanted to break-up. Our client, Mr. Summer, wants to avoid this scenario.\rViolent temper and cold heart is a dangerous combination. Love can change into hate very quickly.\r\rWhat better way to destroy winter than with fire?\r\rGood Luck, 47.",
